en.title: FusionExcel Sponsors RM 30,000 to Myanmar Chess Federation!
en.content: FusionExcel is proud to sponsor RM 30,000 ( cash and products) to the Myanmar Chess Federation who is holding their annual Myanmar Chess Festival 2009 in Yangon between 25th October - 08th November 2009. Receiving the mock cheque from FE's Founder CEO Paul Ting and Founder Director KS Lee is the President of the Myanmar Chess Federation, Maung Maung Lwin who is also an FusionExcel Leader together with his upline, FusionExcel Executive Director Jasen Khoo.
